CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 3, 1957, pg. A8 reads: "Guest Of Frogs - These young socialites were among those joining in the festivities Monday night, when the sons and daughters of the Frogs sponsored their annual affair at the Alpha House. Above are Bobby Williams, Boots Bray, Patricia Lee, Ronald King, Lindsay Wilson, Frank W. Clark, Virginia Norman and Thomas Angell. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Bobby Williams, LouJeanne "Bootsie" Bray, Patricia Lee, Ronald King, Lindsay Wilson, Frank W. Clark, Virginia Norman, and Thomas Angell gathered in Alpha Psi Alpha House for junior FROGS event
